On 9/14/05, zzapper <david@tvis.co.uk> wrote:
> But is there an option to switch off case-sensitivity?
>=20

Does this do what you want?

# Match case-insensitively
zstyle ':completion:*' matcher-list 'm:{a-z}=3D{A-Z}'

